::Zeus/Prowl::

Zeus growls as his missile misses its mark. The newcomer turns in the air, 
heading for Shadow Wing. Two more missiles get ready to fire.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Heading for Sixshot, Prowl sees Zeus flying under him. He folds his wings, 
diving at Zeus.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Zeus grunts as talons sink into his back, sending him and Prowl falling 
toward the ground, the missiles that Zeus had shot missing and hitting trees.
